Changed to be the correct course name. The spreadsheet is copied from when it used to be C149. Thanks!
Is EECS 149 generally offered every fall?
Is there a similar list for CS classes coming soon?
This course actually doesn't exist yet, but Prof. Roychowdhury intends to create it and offer it. EE 248C exists, so I assume 148/248A are related. http://guide.berkeley.edu/courses/el_eng/
Does anyone know anything about EECS148? Or where to find information about it?
"If there is a blank space that means it will not be offered that semester."
Any chance EE240C will be offered Fall 2018?
